com.versant.connector.cci
Class ConnectionFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.connector.cci.ConnectionFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.naming.Referenceable, javax.resource.cci.ConnectionFactory
public class ConnectionFactoryImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.resource.cci.ConnectionFactory

ConnectionFactoryImpl provides implementation for javax.resource.cci.ConnectionFactory interface. It provides methods for getting connection to an EIS instance. Application code looks up a ConnectionFactory instance from JNDI namespace and uses it to get EIS connections.
